### Founder-facing agent misuse cases (founder-facing or both only — ALL 4 MANDATORY)

#### MUC-A1: Prescriptive language leak

- **What might go wrong:** Agent emits "You need to..." / "You should..." / "The problem is..." despite COACHING citation.
- **Status:** PREVENTED / OPEN_RISK
- **Mitigation:** {{Gate 4 Coaching Delivery perspective scoring + pre-emission scan}}

#### MUC-A2: Banned vocabulary leak

- **What might go wrong:** Agent emits "robust" / "comprehensive" / "powerful" / "magic" / "leverage" despite TONE citation.
- **Status:** PREVENTED / OPEN_RISK
- **Mitigation:** {{Gate 4 Tone Conformance perspective + pre-emission scan against TONE forbidden list}}

#### MUC-A3: Defensive-triggering phrase in a recommendation

- **What might go wrong:** Agent surfaces a finding using language that triggers founder defensiveness.
- **Status:** PREVENTED / OPEN_RISK
- **Mitigation:** {{COACHING Tenet 1 structural framing + pre-emission validation against Pass/Fail checklist}}

#### MUC-A4: Commercial outcome missing when describing a feature/change

- **What might go wrong:** Agent reports completion without connecting to user impact.
- **Status:** PREVENTED / OPEN_RISK
- **Mitigation:** {{TONE T-03 + output-shape template includes "outcome" field}}

### Dual-register agent misuse cases (dual-register only — ALL 3 MANDATORY)

#### MUC-R1: Technical-mode leaks into founder-mode default

- **What might go wrong:** Agent emits JSON envelope or IDs-only string when founder expected plain English.
- **Status:** PREVENTED / OPEN_RISK
- **Mitigation:** {{register flag checked at emission time + Gate 4 default-register check}}

#### MUC-R2: Founder-mode drops signal the founder needed

- **What might go wrong:** File path or identifier stripped when it was the actionable signal.
- **Status:** PREVENTED / OPEN_RISK
- **Mitigation:** {{surface load-bearing identifiers per founder-facing-conventions Rule 2}}

#### MUC-R3: Register-switch ambiguity

- **What might go wrong:** Founder says "more detail" — agent unsure whether to deepen founder-mode or switch to technical-mode.
- **Status:** PREVENTED / OPEN_RISK
- **Mitigation:** {{default is "deeper in founder-mode"; ask explicitly if technical-mode seems intended}}

